In the previous post I mentioned that Cypress does not support multi-tab testing. But is there anything we can do in some cases? Let&rsquo;s find out. Let&rsquo;s say that we need to perform an end to end test of our blog. We want to be sure that included github link is working properly. First we need to visit our blog:
cy.visit(&lsquo;https://thebugger.io/');
Then, in order to check if github link is working, we need to click it and see if the outcome of this action is correct.
